data.description: Charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom ranch-style home nestled in the Highlands neighborhood. This thoughtfully updated residence boasts a spacious galley kitchen, A mudroom with a convenient laundry area adds to the functionality of daily living. The heart of the home is an expansive open living and dining area, providing a versatile space to relax and entertain. A focal point of this home is the, freshly updated primary bathroom, offering a serene retreat for your personal comfort. Outdoor living is equally inviting, with a fully fenced front yard and back yard, ensuring privacy and security. The concrete patio at the front of the home serves as a welcoming outdoor gathering spot. Experience the perfect blend of comfort and convenience.
